{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"74edd74a6c","title":"陶铸与西安交通大学和重庆大学同学的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba45295f54","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"74edd74a6c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对话","id":"314ad57c4d","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"造反运动和派别斗争","id":"d48f0ea3e8","type":"主题"},{"name":"陶铸","id":"dbcf15bd08","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"489fec27f2","name":"陶铸"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"657bb21e8d","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"一九六六年北京化工学院《红色宣传员》战斗组、北京经济学院无产阶级革命团、北京市东方红印刷厂革命造反联络处、化工部化学工业出版社印刷厂联合汇编《无产阶级文化大革命参考资料（1）》。"}],"contents":[{"id":"cf6e279ed8","type":"title","text":"陶铸与西安交通大学和重庆大学同学的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"158e3dd191","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：八月二十一日下午四时半，地点：中南海。交大和重大部分同学在返校前请见陶铸同志，现将谈话记录整理如下。〗","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8cea1123cc","type":"paragraph","text":"问：他们说我们到北京来是反革命。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f3302006f","type":"paragraph","text":"答：说你们是反革命的本身就是反革命的口号。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cfcf3047d4","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“誓死保卫西北局”、“誓死保卫陕西省委”的口号对不对？","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ad48ce4d5","type":"paragraph","text":"答：是错误的，只能提“誓死保卫党中央”、“誓死保卫毛主席”。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c5e99c5fea","type":"paragraph","text":"问：关于省委改组问题？","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5881573974","type":"paragraph","text":"答：陕西省委改组要报告党中央，由中央决定，这要报告党中央，报告毛主席，由毛主席决定，你们完全有权利提这个意见。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cbb8113def","type":"paragraph","text":"问：大字报贴到街上就算反革命吗？","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ef9ca917b1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：不算，大字报可以贴在街上，也可以在街上辩论。你们可以上街游行、宣传、辩论，把大字报贴在街上是革命的，学生在街上游行示威是革命的，不是反革命的，是可以的，也可以贴标语在街上。十六条已经指出，要文斗不要武斗。工人、农民打学生不对，工人农民可以支援，不要打人。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dbe315357f","type":"paragraph","text":"问：我们回西安下火车要挨打的，怎么办？","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"34ee14cbb1","type":"paragraph","text":"答：你们越挨打就越是革命，我们过去搞革命是要杀头的。现在你们挨打算得了什么，现在挨打是为了革命的。他们打不要紧，他们是反革命的，他们一定会被你们打倒的。过去革命还是有生命危险，还要抛头颅洒鲜血，你们现在挨一下打没什么。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"04fc126b86","type":"paragraph","text":"问：“誓死保卫西北局”、“誓死保卫陕西省委”的口号对不对？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2391b56550","type":"paragraph","text":"答：陕西省委改组要报告党中央，由中央决定，这要报告党中央，报告毛主席，由毛主席决定，你们完全有权利提这个意见。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3169616e3b","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"74edd74a6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"610f654d8c","type":"paragraph","text":"陶铸与西安交通大学和重庆大学同学的谈话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenk